description: The Board of Managers of OneKey® MLS named Richard Haggerty as the new Chief Executive Officer for OneKey® MLS. Haggerty, who currently serves as CEO of the Hudson Gateway Association of REALTORS® and as President and Chief Strategic Growth Officer of OneKey® MLS, will succeed Jim Speer, the current CEO, on Jan. 1, 2023. Speer has announced his plans for retirement at the end of this year.
title: OneKey® MLS Appoints Richard Haggerty as CEO
